name: Crunch - Slag Ronin 5.5"
description:
Crunch is a Custom 5.5" Croney Platform using Polymer Clay, Mixed Media, & Acrylic. He is One of a Kind.
       The last remaining vestiges of once great warriors, The Ronin of the Slag Wasteland, are all that remain of the Great War that burned that cursed place onto the face of the world of Penopticon. Slag Ronin however are not to be underestimated, for vestiges of their former selves they may be, venerable warriors they still are, now plying their trade as swords for hire across the land. While highly skilled paid mercenaries the true purpose that drives a Slag Ronin is to reclaim his honor, often along with ceremonial armor, weaponry, and decapitated head, that was stripped from his once lifeless form. Authorities & citizens alike search for the truth behind dark rumors of who may be reanimating these long dead heroes & villians, and to what true purpose.

Part of Alexa Hartford's 'Fureez Mascots: Smoke Break' Series 'Plague' is a hand painted one of a kind custom Kid Robot 4" Munny & 2.5" Labbit, using Polymer Clay, Mixed Media, & Acrylic. 
       See a more cynical (and likely realistic) side of your favorite Mascot, and collect them all caught and frozen in time in the middle of their Smoke Break.

name: The Maniacal DR. Hoggles
description:
This Piece includes 2 customized resins;    Mutagenic lab assistants 'Squirm' Platforms. DR. Hoggles is a Custom 4" Kid Robot Kracka. 
         A former Professor of Super Science at Penopticon University, The Maniacal Dr Hoggles, in his descent into madness, lost his tenure as well as his original eyes. Now a recluse of epic proportions he carries out the machinations of his dark plans in secret from the spires of Castle Hoggshire, alone aside from his faithful but often unwilling interns turned Mutagenic freaks, as well as indentured lab assistants: now known as The brothers Squirthog Rip & Snort.

name: Tumble the TruffPunk
description:
Tumble The TruffPunk. A Hogcore Kid for Life, Tumble give No F**ks,  whether hanging with the crew on the mean streets, drinking 40s on the corner, or thrashing at Hogcore shows.
      Tumble is a one of a kind, hand painted, 4" Kid Robot Kracka, Customized using Polymer Clay, Mixed Media, & Acrylic.
     Series: Truffalo Empire
     Signed: YES

description:

Capt. Lockjaw is a one of a kind custom 4" Kid Robot Kracka: using Polymer Clay, Mixed Media, & Acrylic.

name: Pengman - DIY
description:
These formerly human citizens of Penopticon, through there gluttony and affinity for cold weather, are becoming humanoid Pengmen! 
     This one piece DIY Platform is cast in white Resin and is ~5in tall. 
Super Cute and Great for customization!

name: Clear Colored Sheople
description: 2.5" Clear Colored Resin Sheople, are available in Red, Green, Blue, and Water Clear. Custom color requests are welcome, just hit us up on the "Contact' page and we'll do our best to match what you have in mind.

name: Sheople
description:
Ever heard of the Mass Populace of humanity referred to as 'Sheep'? Well in the dualistic world of Penopticon, this metaphor has taken on a more literal meaning. The people of Penopticon are becoming Sheople! And with all vestiges of original thoughts having fled from there brains they are now left with nothing but a vague sense of confusion, and an intangible feeling of loss likely derived from their lack of opposable  thumbs. 

 These 2.5" hand painted Resin Sheople each come with their own unique and confused facial expression. Customs on the Sheople platform are available upon request, hit us up on the 'Contact' page.

name: Croney DIY
description: This 5in Resin Platform comes with the arms pegged and holed, but unlike the other Cronies, the DIYs are shipped with the arms unglued so you can pose them yourself! Yay! A dab of any kind of superglue works great, but if your not comfortable with gluing just select the 'pre-posed' option and we'll be happy to ship them with the arms pre-glued and posed just like in the photo.

name: Croney - Clear Colored Resin
description:
